{"tid":704016,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求7.1遊行維園出發 盧偉聰：東角道加入者可能非法集會","createTime":"2018-06-16T06:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T13:38:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac3d6e5b007a2dbc2f3b6f06db38e44caf57f5c","tid":704016,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:10:34.000Z","msg":"警方就7.1遊行向民陣發出不反對通知書，但要求出發地點改為維園草坪，而非民陣要求的銅鑼灣東角道。警務處處長盧偉聰今早回應指，根據警方往年經驗和證據，認為維園才是最適合人群聚集的地方，「東角道車多人多，同埋係星期日，根本上係唔適合咁大型嘅聚集」，重申警方要求更改地點是為了公共安全和市民的人身安全，呼籲市民聽從警方指示。<br />\n<br />\n民陣呼籲參與7.1遊行市民自行在東角道加入，盧就稱市民要慎重考慮，「因為任何參與呢啲活動嘅人，係有可能參與非法集會」，強調市民若在其他地方中途加入，只會擾亂遊行過程。"},{"pid":"290d8d42908d73e9be31387373fa44eae725ecf1","tid":704016,"uid":116330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n民陣呼籲參與7.1遊行市民自行在東角道加入，盧就稱市民要慎重考慮<span style=\"color: red;\">，「因為任何參與呢啲活動嘅人，係有可能參與非法集會」</span>，強調市民若在其他地方中途加入，只會擾亂遊行過程。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe222ca9e3751116fbc42ece8bdf2e00ba7bb42f","tid":704016,"uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"r